text: Kazarma () is a rural locality (a selo) in Starotukmaklinsky Selsoviet, Kushnarenkovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 510 as of 2010. There are 5 streets. == Geography == It is located 29 km from Kushnarenkovo, 8 km from Starye Tukmakly. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kushnarenkovsky District
title: Kazarma, Kushnarenkovsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
